# Liabilities Non Current Provision Deferred Tax Amount

## identifier
de8942

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of provision for non-current deferred tax liabilities, as determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.NonCurrentProvisionDeferredTax.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
